  person can't read it (and then you have to go to a real<br>
  headshrinker and pay big bucks). Many of the V.A.     <br>
  Hospitals (AND THAT IS ANOTHER THREAD TO BE MADE) have<br>
  info and groups, etc. on PTSD.  Try:<br>
  http://www.long-beach.va.gov/ptsd/stress.html  for a<br>
  start.<br><br>
  For information regarding disability claims or of a more<br>
